    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hearthlands is a medieval/fantasy city-building real time strategy game in which you take a role of a king in a procedurally generated world. You can not control your subjects directly; instead you focus on city-building, resource management, diplomacy, magic and other things a  typical king deals with on a daily basis. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is very flexible: you can build a powerful realm and rule the lands with an iron grip, or establish a humble fishermen village. Or create a trading empire. Or found a small, but well-defended outpost or a raider's camp. Or become a host of a wizard's manor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All characters, from a humble hauler to a powerful wizard have their own minds and behavior patterns. Sometimes it is interesting just to watch people scurry about minding their own business. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a medieval city;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game the way you like it: experiment with sandbox settings or play a campaign mode (ex. Polish localization);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your people happy by providing them with necessary resources and services;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources, produce goods and build industries;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See reports and tune up your economy;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build an army and protect your city from monsters and invasions;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade and conduct diplomacy with neighbouring realms, or go to war with them; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Research technologies and cast spells;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself by going after one of the many achievements. </p></li></ul>",
